<h2>Write your review</h2>
<!--<p class="heading__meta">This step is optional</p>-->
<hr />

<p>Your review must be honest, respectful and useful to other patients. We won’t publish your review if it breaks our rules: </p>

<div class="panel">
  <div class="panel__content panel__content--half">
    <h3>Do</h3>
    <ul class="list--check">
      <li>give as much detail as possible to help other patients make a decision</li>
      <li>back up your opinions with facts</li>
      <li>be polite, even if you’re angry</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
  <div class="panel__content panel__content--half">
    <h3>Don’t</h3>
    <ul class="list--cross">
      <li>try too hard to influence people - for example by telling them not to use the surgery</li>
      <li>write about something that happened over 2 years ago</li>
      <li>leave more than 1 review about a single incident</li>
      <li>identify people - for example by including their name, gender or contact details</li>
      <li>be obscene, racist, sexist or homophobic</li>
      <li>include anything that could break the law or affect legal proceedings</li>
      <li>WRITE IN CAPITALS LIKE THIS</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</div>

<p>You can also:</p>
<ul>
  <li><a href="/2_2_read_other_reviews">read reviews by other patients</a></li>
  <li><a href="2_3_rules_on_writing_reviews">read full rules on writing reviews</a></li>
</ul>


<div class="section">
  <form action="2_write_your_review_v2" method="POST">
    <div class="section">
      <div class="form-line">
        <label for="body" class="form-label"><h3>Your review</h3></label>
        <span class="form-label__hint" id="hintId">3,000 characters maximum</span>
        <textarea rows="17" class="form-textbox" name="body" placeholder=" ">{{body}}</textarea>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="button__spacing">
      <input type="submit" class="button" value="Next">
    </div>
  </form>
</div>

{{> components/back_link
  label="Back"
}}

